inputs.text:
"0": "Two hands reaching towards each other, fingertips almost touching, set against a backdrop of a warm sunset, symbolizing the beginning of human connection and the potential it holds to enrich our lives.",
"60": "A close-up of two people deeply engaged in conversation, their expressions earnest and attentive, with a soft focus on the background to emphasize the soul-reaching depth of their interaction.",
"120": "A group of friends laughing together, their heads thrown back in genuine amusement, captured in a moment of uninhibited joy, highlighting the shared laughter that bonds people together.",
"180": "A comforting scene of one person offering a supportive hug to another, in a setting that feels intimate and safe, representing the unconditional support that is a cornerstone of meaningful connections.",
"240": "An image of a well-worn path leading over hills, with footprints in both directions, symbolizing the transcendent nature of true connections that overcome the barriers of time and distance.",
"300": "A collage of various friendships, from childhood playmates to elderly companions, each image capturing a moment of connection, illustrating the idea that every friendship offers a chance to deepen our experience of life.",
"360": "An open door leading to a cozy, inviting living room, where a group of people are gathered in comfortable conversation, encouraging us to open our hearts and homes to nurture relationships.",
"420": "A network of stars connected by lines against a night sky, representing the invisible bonds that hold us together and elevate us, mirroring the interconnectedness of human relationships.",
"480": "A series of small, candid moments: a shared glance, a comforting squeeze of the hand, laughter over coffee, each capturing the essence of what it means to live a life rich with connections.",
"540": "A heart-shaped photo collage on a wall, filled with pictures of loved ones, friends, and cherished moments, reminding us to value and express gratitude for the relationships that make us feel alive.",
"600": "A final image of a serene beach at dusk, with two sets of footprints leading together into the distance, symbolizing the journey of shared moments and love given and received, the true treasures of the soul."
